We as a town are proud of the accomplishments of our talented resident, Brody Cobb.  He is a talented musician, poet and guitar builder.
Brody Cobb is a lifetime resident of Richland, has strong family ties to the town and is a talented musician and well known guitar builder.

Both the city of Richland and the Stewart county are proud of our resident Brody Cobb.  It has come to our attention that you have been cyber bullying the City of Richland and removing their addition of our local hero to Wikipedia.  Please stop.  It’s not fair to the City, County, Brody and the public.
